flowchart TD
    A([Idea or problem surfaces\nTesting · new template · feedback]) --> B

    B[Claude.ai\nThink through spec\nMake product decisions\nDraft implementation prompt]

    B --> C[Claude Code\nTerminal-based implementation\nGuided by prompt from Claude.ai]

    C --> D[TypeScript check\nnpx tsc --noEmit]
    D --> E{Pass?}
    E -- No --> F[Targeted fix prompt\nto Claude Code]
    F --> D
    E -- Yes --> G[Lint\nnpm run lint]
    G --> H{Pass?}
    H -- No --> F
    H -- Yes --> I[Commit + push\ngit add · git commit · git push]

    I --> J[Open pull request\nGitHub]

    J --> K[GitHub Copilot\nAutomated PR review\nSuggestions flagged]

    K --> L{Suggestions\nto act on?}

    L -- Yes --> M[Human review\nEvaluate suggestions]
    M --> N[Pass feedback to\nClaude or Claude Code]
    N --> C

    L -- No --> O[Merge PR\nGitHub]

    O --> P[Cloudflare Pages\nAuto-deploy on merge]

    P --> Q[Test in browser\nLive app review]

    Q --> R[Update docs\nchangelog · docs/decisions.md · docs/rules.md]

    R --> S{New idea or\nproblem?}
    S -- Yes --> A
    S -- No --> T([Done for now])

    style A fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style T fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style B fill:#c47a1e,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style C fill:#c47a1e,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style K fill:#6e3fa3,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style M fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style O fill:#1b4332,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style P fill:#f38020,color:#fff,stroke:none
